title: Robert Blundell
text: Robert Blundell (19 April 1896 – 11 February 1940) was an Australian <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He played five <a href="first-class%20cricket">first-class</a> matches for <a href="Western%20Australia%20cricket%20team">Western Australia</a> between 1921/22 and 1924/25.
